{"tid":2495862,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"54歲男子昨昏迷不治 月初曾接種科興疫苗","createTime":"2021-04-19T12:17:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T12:27:47.000Z","uid":21470,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"52566c3dd97c529dfe00c2ea347d09ca6c2e5d19","tid":2495862,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T12:17:45.000Z","msg":"54歲男子昏迷不治 月初曾接種疫苗<br />\n<br />\n一名54歲男子昨日昏迷不治，他本初曾接種新冠疫苗；消息指他沒有長期病患，月初在沙田源禾路體育館接種第一劑科興疫苗。北區醫院表示，病人昨日凌晨被發現昏迷，由救護車送到北區醫院急症室，搶救無效死亡。他本月2日曾接種新冠疫苗，院方已將個案呈報衛生署。<br />\n<br />\n本港近日累計有17名曾接種新冠疫苗的人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2387897\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2387897&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqx3%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=fe01fe2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2387897</a>"},{"pid":"111b1dbd596634398a296de08d90a7f58cd83fb2","tid":2495862,"uid":361751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T12:19:29.000Z","msg":"又中頭獎<br />\n<br />\n但派彩未？"},{"pid":"959b42cd9f61db1dd37f23d101cde53511f70fdf","tid":2495862,"uid":387826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T12:20:36.000Z","msg":"勁過武肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"176a40f800ea6e79ff5ead41895ac98e1a20865a","tid":2495862,"uid":268591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T12:20:55.000Z","msg":"科興有效率越黎越高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b64fe219eac43119074eb1bb57b301c56a4fbabc","tid":2495862,"uid":198389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T12:22:04.000Z","msg":"第幾個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n已經唔想數"},{"pid":"8b96cde3cf13b6d03f6a41335466a7409b06a7e7","tid":2495862,"uid":134686